sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Title } from "../components/Title" import { Container, Header } from 'semantic-ui-react' export const Bookshelf = () => { return ( <> <div className="ui container"> <Container fluid> <Header as='h2'>See your Saved Title</Header> <p> Whether you're looking for something new or wanting to remind yourself to check out that new Nora Roberts novel your roommate recommended, our search service has just what you need! </p> </Container> </div> </> ) }
